            <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="entry:37;99:20" colname="col1" dita-ot:x="1" dita-ot:y="13"><codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="codeph:21;99:28">N-N</codeph></entry>
            <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="entry:38;100:20" colname="col2" dita-ot:x="2" dita-ot:y="13">Both rules must pass (logical AND). The second N is the
            rule that follows the first.</entry>
            <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="entry:39;102:20" colname="col3" dita-ot:x="3" dita-ot:y="13"><codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="codeph:22;102:28">1-2</codeph> — rules 1 AND 2 must both pass</entry>
          </row>
