    <section id="recipe-simple" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="section:1;108:33">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="title:3;109:14">Recipe: Single rule check</title>
      <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;110:39">"steps": "S-1,1-E"</codeblock>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="p:1;111:10">Start with rule 1. Rule 1's result ends the workflow.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="recipe-conditional" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="section:2;114:38">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="title:4;115:14">Recipe: Conditional check (run rule B only when rule A passes)</title>
      <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="codeblock:2;116:39">"steps": "S-A,A-D,T-B,F-sentinel,B-M,sentinel-M,M-E"</codeblock>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="p:2;117:10">Rule A is the decision. If True, rule B runs and its result feeds into
      merge. If False, the sentinel rule (a known-passing rule) feeds into merge.
      Merge ends the workflow.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="recipe-and" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="section:3;122:30">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="title:5;123:14">Recipe: Both rules must pass (AND)</title>
      <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="codeblock:3;124:39">"steps": "S-1,1-2,2-E"</codeblock>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_workflow-steps.dita" xtrc="p:3;125:10">Start with rule 1. Rule 1 must pass before rule 2 is checked. Rule 2's
      result ends the workflow.</p>
    </section>

